# Testing

- Test names describe security behavior: `test_unknown_tool_is_denied_by_policy`.
- Every invariant: allow path + deny path where applicable.
- Do not mock away the control under test.
- Deterministic; no external APIs or network (except local FastAPI in integration tests).
- Vulnerable-path tests use simulation only; protected-path tests prove the control plane blocks unsafe behavior.

When adding a control, add tests first or in the same change. If a control has no test, it does not exist.
